text.tspan: Value of imports and exports, World
Illustrates the total value of imports/exports as a share of world GDP. The total value of imports/exports as a share of
World GDP is shown for World Bank income categories, and OWID continents. Country series display the total value
of imports/exports as a share of country GDP.
Source: CEPII exports - Two Centuries of Bilateral Trade and Gravity Data: 1827-2014 (2016), CEPII imports - Two Centuries of Bilateral Trade
